################################################################################
# Basic OS and package management stuff
################################################################################

# Kernel headers, sudo and building tools

i  aptitude            - terminal-based package manager  
i  sudo                - Provide limited super user privileges to specific users
i  linux-headers-amd64 - Header files for Linux amd64 configuration (meta-package)
i  build-essential     - Informational list of build-essential packages
i  pkg-config          - manage compile and link flags for libraries

# Install laptop power management and basic firmware

i  laptop-mode-tools      - Tools for Power Savings based on battery/AC status
i  firmware-linux-free    - Binary firmware for various drivers in the Linux kernel
i  firmware-linux-nonfree - Binary firmware for various drivers in the Linux kernel (meta-package)
i  intel-microcode        - Processor microcode firmware for Intel CPUs

################################################################################
# Desktop environment and working stuff
################################################################################

# KDE and yakuake

i  kde-full                - complete KDE Software Compilation for end users
i  kdesudo                 - sudo frontend for KDE
i  yakuake                 - Quake-style terminal emulator based on KDE Konsole technology

# Console

i  zsh                     - shell with lots of features
i  zsh-syntax-highlighting - Fish shell like syntax highlighting for zsh
i  tmux                    - terminal multiplexer

# Git and code tools

i  git                     - fast, scalable, distributed revision control system
i  gitk                    - fast, scalable, distributed revision control system (revision tree visualizer)
i  git-gui                 - fast, scalable, distributed revision control system (GUI)
i  kompare                 - file difference viewer
i  cloc                    - statistics utility to count lines of code

# Misc

i  mesa-utils              - Miscellaneous Mesa GL utilities
i  chromium                - web browser
i  ffmpeg                  - Tools for transcoding, streaming and playing of multimedia files
i  tree                    - displays an indented directory tree, in color
i  xclip                   - command line interface to X selections

# blacklist nouveau
i  bbswitch-dkms
i  bumblebee-nvidia
i  primus
